latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello Everyone , This is a simple dance cover video of beautiful song of one of my favs Shankuraj's beautiful soulful song "Alakananda". Hope u enjoy this video. It's a very simple because I have no video camera I shoot this on my own phone. 

Hope you will enjoy my version of dance on this beautiful song. Hope you will enjoy watching my video as much as I have enjoyed while dancing. 

Song - Alakananda
Singer - Shankuraj Konwar
Music Composed and Produced by - Tonmoy Krypton
Lyrics - Maitrayee Patar

Choreography -  Himashree Handique

Edited by -  Partha Protim Chutia
